Package: gl-app-wattline
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Keith <keith@kodi.tv>
Section: gl
Priority: optional
Depends: wattlined
Description: GL.iNet admin-panel (oui) app for Wattline. Adds a native entry under Applications with live battery/port telemetry and DC/USB-C controls, backed by the wattlined REST API via an oui-httpd RPC shim. No separate login (uses the panel session).
